## Data Flow: Complete Action Loop

```
1. GOAL INPUT
   User → gRPC CreateGoal("Book Delhi→Mumbai June 5, cheapest")
        → ans-nerves Goal Decomposer (LLM)
        → GoalSpec { sub_goals: [navigate, fill-origin, fill-dest, fill-dates,
                    click-search, parse-results, sort-price, select-cheapest,
                    fill-passenger, click-book] }
        → ans-daemon Goal State Manager stores, broadcasts via NATS

2. SESSION CREATION
   ans-daemon: create session for goal, launch Chromium, navigate to start URL
        → Immune System classifies page on arrival (distractions flagged)
        → DOM Distiller runs (mode: input-fields for search form)
        → Arrow IPC: screenshot captured → shared memory
        → NATS: ans.goal.<id>.update, ans.session.<id>.action

3. PERCEPTION (5 Eyes in parallel)
   Vision Eye:      Screenshot(Arrow IPC) → Claude/GPT-4o → VisionReport
   DOM Reader Eye:  DistilledDom(gRPC) → structured element list
   Diff Eye:        Rust diff → enriched with semantic interpretation
   Goal Verifier:   All reports + goal state → "Did action advance goal?"
   Error Detector:  All reports → FailureType + RecoveryStrategy

4. CROSS-EYE SYNTHESIS
   Cross-Eye Coordinator receives all 5 EyeReports via NATS
        → Identifies contradictions (Vision says button visible, DOM says disabled)
        → Produces unified SituationalSnapshot
        → Published to NATS: ans.eye.cross_eye.synthesis

5. DECISION
   Decision Engine receives RoutedSignal
        → Embeds current context → vector
        → gRPC QueryBestActions(context_embedding, k=5) → Rust LanceDB
        → Returns top-5 historically successful (action, tool) for this context
        → LLM selects best among them (or overrides if context is novel)
        → Executes action via gRPC ExecuteAction

6. VERIFICATION
   After action executes:
        → Page Diff runs automatically (on distilled DOM)
        → Goal Verifier checks: "Did the diff mean goal advanced?"
        → If YES: update goal sub-state, proceed to next step
        → If NO: Error Detector classifies failure → RecoveryStrategy → informed retry

7. SCORING
   Decision Engine scores the executed action:
        composite = outcome*0.35 + result*0.30 + error_penalty*0.20 + business*0.15
        → gRPC StoreScore → Rust LanceDB (appended, vector-indexed)
        → NATS: ans.decision.scored
```

