| **5: Decision Intelligence** | 13-16 | Scoring engine (outcome/result/error/business), LanceDB storage, vector search, gRPC service | 1 Rust, 1 Python | Decisions scored, stored, searchable |
| **6: Immune System** | 14-17 | Heuristic classifier, WASM ML runner, immune pipeline, model training pipeline | 1 Rust, 0.5 Python | Harmful actions blocked within 6ms |
| **7: Signal Router + Goal State** | 15-17 | NATS router, schema registry, shared goal state (Arc\<RwLock\>), state persistence | 1 Rust | Events route, goals share state |
| **8: Dashboard + CLI** | 16-19 | Next.js dashboard, live view, decision timeline, debug visualizer, `ans` CLI | 1 TypeScript | Live dashboard, CLI tools |
| **9: Hardening** | 18-22 | E2E scenarios, perf benchmarks, memory profiling, error injection, security review, docs | 5 | Production-ready |

### Critical Path
```
Foundation → Browser Control → DOM/Diff (parallel with Vision Eye)
→ Coordination → Decision Intelligence → Immune System → E2E = 20 weeks
```

